  RowBox[{"(*", 
   RowBox[{"This", " ", "obtains", " ", "all", " ", "the", " ", "full", " ", 
    RowBox[{"references", " ", "[", 
     RowBox[{"@", "reference"}], "]"}]}], "*)"}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.862556681951933*^9, 3.862556689714443*^9}, {
