22fed6377649"],

Cell["\<\
Equation references in pandoc have the form
 {#complement theorem .theorem} to label
 [2](#complement theorem){reference-type=\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]ref\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]
reference=\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]complement theorem\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]} \
to reference and have to be changed to 
<a name=\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]comp\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]>Theorem 7<a/> \
for marking as anchor
and [7](#comp) for making link\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.893611399546937*^9, 3.893611453569108*^9}, {
  3.8944515046589513`*^9, 3.894451542297805*^9}, {3.894454712315499*^9, 
